# truncate

##### Empty a file

   truncate  foobar.txt

##### Create arbitrary big file full of zeroes but done in a second

   truncate  size 1G bigfile.txt

##### Empty a file

   truncate  -s 0 file.txt

##### Create a file of a given size in linux

   truncate  -s 1M file

##### Create arbitrary big file full of zeroes but done in a second

   truncate  size 1G bigfile.txt

##### Empty a file

   truncate  -s 0 file.txt

##### Create a file of a given size in linux

   truncate  -s 1M file
